y.com/pages/negotiating_a_salary.jpg"><meta name="description" content="How to negotiate a salary and get what you deserve. Learn how to ask for more money in an interview and beyond! (Extra information on negotiating perks and benefits!)"><meta property="og:description" content="How to negotiate a salary and get what you deserve. Learn how to ask for more money in an interview and beyond! (Extra information on negotiating perks and benefits!)"><meta property="og:title" content="How to Negotiate a Salary: 30+ Tips and Examples"><style>.li-bold {font-weight: 600; font-size: 20px;}</style><meta property="workz:page:id" content="606"><meta property="og:type" content="article"><meta property="og:url" content="https://zety.com/blog/how-to-negotiate-a-salary"><meta property="og:site_name" content="zety"><meta property="article:published_time" content="2018-08-02T13:01:06+01:00"><meta property="article:modified_time" content="2019-09-29T18:33:25+01:00"><meta property="article:author" content="Chaymae Samir"><meta property="article:section" content=""><meta property="article:tag" content=""><meta property="article:publisher" content="https://www.facebook.com/zety.your.resume.builder/"><meta property="twitter:title" content="How to Negotiate a Salary: 30+ Tips and Examples"><meta property="twitter:description" content="How to Negotiate a Salary: 30+ Tips and Examples"><meta property="twitter:image" content="//cdn-images.zety.com/pages/how_to_negotiate_salary.jpg?w=1950&h=500&fit=crop&auto=compress"><meta property="article:content_tier" content=""><meta property="fb:app_id" content="1766296813589440"><meta property="fb:admins" content=""><meta property="p:domain_verify" content=""><link rel="canonical" href="how-to-negotiate-a-salary"><script type="application/ld+json">{
